{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-template-js","path":"/post/ai-assisted-fraud-investigation-man-machine","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"id":"f0addd57-15f9-5fc6-bfd3-a64ba994fd9e","title":"AI-Assisted Fraud Investigation: Man &#038; Machine","content":"<p><img src=\"https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-Logo-Las-Vegas.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 636px) 100vw, 636px\" srcset=\"https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-Logo-Las-Vegas-200x109.png 200w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-Logo-Las-Vegas-300x163.png 300w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-Logo-Las-Vegas-400x218.png 400w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-Logo-Las-Vegas-600x326.png 600w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-Logo-Las-Vegas.png 636w\" alt=\"ACFE Fraud Conference 2018 Logo Las Vegas\" width=\"636\" height=\"346\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" srcset=\"https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-200x106.png 200w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-300x160.png 300w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-400x213.png 400w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-600x319.png 600w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-768x409.png 768w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018-800x426.png 800w, https://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adding-Machine-Intelligence-to-Fraud-Investigations-ACFE-Fraud-Conference-2018.png 940w\" alt=\"Adding Machine Intelligence to Fraud Investigations ACFE Fraud Conference 2018\" width=\"940\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p>DataVisor&#8217;s Director of Strategy, Igor Bidny presented about AI-Assisted Fraud Investigations at the ACFE Global Fraud Conference in June 2018. Igor introduces Artificial Intelligence to the audience, breaking down the major sub fields and then focusing specifically on machine learning and its various types. Next, Igor covers various fraud detection methods, including rules-based solutions, supervised learning, and unsupervised learning, and describes each method&#8217;s pros and cons. Lastly, Igor shares case studies of how modern, coordinated fraud attacks happen and how unsupervised machine learning is uniquely able to detect them, often before they happen.</p>\n<p><iframe style=\"border: 1px solid #CCC; border-width: 1px; margin-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"//www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/key/xn2gjzVvdUZfZU\" width=\"595\" height=\"485\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"> </iframe> <strong> <a title=\"DataVisor ACFE Fraud Conference - AI-Assisted Fraud Investigation\" href=\"//www.slideshare.net/DataVisor/datavisor-acfe-fraud-conference-aiassisted-fraud-investigation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DataVisor ACFE Fraud Conference &#8211; AI-Assisted Fraud Investigation</a> </strong> from <strong><a href=\"https://www.slideshare.net/DataVisor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DataVisor</a></strong></p>\n","excerpt":"<p>DataVisor&#8217;s Director of Strategy Igor Bidny discusses cutting edge trends and techniques for applying machine learning to fraud investigation. With the rise of coordinated, sophisticated attacks, taking advantage of the latest big data and machine learning technology is ever more important.</p>\n","date":"June 25, 2018","author":{"id":"862a718f-703a-590d-b82d-0737780ee98d","name":"Igor Bidny"}}},"pageContext":{"id":14192}}}